{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"edgeMode","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/edgeMode","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>edgeMode</code>属性确定了当核心位于输入图像的边缘或贴近输入图像的边缘时，如何取用颜色值用于扩展输入图像，从而可以应用矩阵操作。</p>\n\n<p>如果没有指定<code>edgeMode</code>属性，等效于值被指定为<code>duplicate</code>。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>无</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><strong>duplicate</strong> | wrap | none</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feConvolveMatrixElementEdgeModeAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"duplicate\">duplicate</dt>\n <dd>它指示输入图像沿着每条边扩展，复制输入图像的给定边缘上的颜色值。</dd>\n <dt id=\"wrap\">wrap</dt>\n <dd>它指示扩展输入图像，从图像相对的边缘取色。</dd>\n <dt id=\"none\">none</dt>\n <dd>它指示扩展输入图像，用 0 作为 RGBA 的像素值。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>edgeMode</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"edgeMode","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/edgemode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/edgemode/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/edgeMode","title":"edgeMode"}],"pageTitle":"edgeMode - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}